name: Parsons v. Motor Freight Express, Appellant, et al.

judges: Before Maxey, C. J., Drew, Linn, Stern, Patterson, Stearns and Hughes, JJ.

opinions.text:
Per Curiam,
This case was tried with that of Schiele v. Motor Freight Express, Inc. 348 Pa. 525, in which the same exceptions were taken, and they have all been disposed of in that case.
Judgment affirmed.

Harry R. Matten, of Matten & Matten, for appellee.
